* Şehzade İsa (23 February 170625 May 1706);
* Şehzade Ali (18 June 170612 September 1706);
* Şehzade Selim (6 September 17074 May 1708);
* Şehzade Murad (4 February 17081 April 1708);
* Şehzade Abdülmelik (12 December 17097 March 1711);
